hancing usability."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements."}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol"}}}